      },
      "raw": "Verse 3 - Trading Bars",
      "text": "Voice 1:\nHat too big.\nVoice 2:\nSpell too strong.\nVoice 1:\nBroom too wild.\nVoice 2:\nNight too long.\nVoice 1:\nWater too high.\nVoice 2:\nDoor won’t move.\nVoice 1:\nWhole tower drowning.\nVoice 2:\nStill in groove.\nVoice 1:\nStrings go sharp.\nVoice 2:\nBassoon go doom.\nVoice 1:\nTimpani hit.\nVoice 2:\nOboes fill the room.\nVoice 1:\nOne little mouse.\nVoice 2:\nBig mistake.\nVoice 1:\nOne little wand.\nVoice 2:\nWhole world shake.\nBoth:\nBlack-and-white world but the money still gold,\nwhole crew slipping while the spell takes hold.\nNo crown, no throne,\njust a hat and a grin,\nthen the broomsticks rise and the nightmare begins.",
      "lines": 38,
      "startT": 189.36,
      "endT": 221.04,
      "bars": 13
