      "raw": "Final Chorus - Bigger Raspy Gang Chant",
      "text": "Brooms in the boiler room,\nwater starts to rise,\nlittle mouse grinning with the stars in his eyes.\nBrooms in the boiler room,\nknocking at the door,\nspell got loose and it hungry for more.\nBlack-and-white world,\nbut the money still gold,\nwhole tower shaking when the wild drums roll.\nBrooms in the boiler room,\nmoon turned blue,\none wrong spell and the whole crew doomed.\nBrooms in the boiler room,\nstill marching,\nstill stomping,\nstill pouring,\nstill watching.",
